node.text: @nh_hid heehee, u won't need it yet...
@belandbray My boy is going to have some mid T3 tests so hopefully it will lessen the weight of SA2. Wish he was Gan Cheong lor... 🤦🏻‍♀️

School holiday officially starts today!⁣
⁣
But this lass is not slacking the least bit after her last #hbl and #sls session yesterday. Because all, if not most, of her usual face-to-face tuition classes have been cancelled, she's worried about catching up with the school curriculum (especially Science where PSLE covers topics taught from P3 onwards), we signed her up for @tenopy.sg at her request.⁣
⁣
@Tenopy.sg specializes in Live Online Tutoring for primary and secondary school students from the comfort of home, conducted by top educators in the industry. I sat in one of the classes Bel had and thought the real-time, live guidance by her tutor was very engaging and clear. From my perspective, I really liked how the curriculum is designed by a former Assistant Dean of NIE to foster the critical thinking skills of students, and the Parents Weekly Report provided after lessons for us to monitor Bel’s progress. These skills-based reports and qualitative feedback are very practical.⁣
⁣
I later asked Bel what she liked about Tenopy’s online classes and here's what she said:⁣
- There are group and voice chats which allow her to ask questions or contribute during the lessons⁣
- Polls and quizzes conducted during lessons are fun ⁣
- Homework can be submitted online for tutors to mark and grade⁣
- All lessons attended are recorded so she can replay them if she missed any lessons, or for revisiting a certain topic⁣
⁣
Seeing is believing so I'd like to invite you and your child to join a COMPLIMENTARY trial class at ⁣
👉 www.tenopy.co/trial⁣
⁣
Remember to sign up using our code <<CGAJHU>> to get $20 credits! If you enjoyed the trial class, you can use the credits to offset the balance during checkout.
👉 www.tenopy.co/signup?referral=CGAJHU
⁣
Better still, this same code can also be used for @Tenopy.sg exciting May Holiday Workshops coming up!⁣
• P3 Literature Workshop⁣
• P4 Creative Writing Workshop⁣
• P5 Philosophy Workshop - Fun topics to be covered; yes, Bel is going! ⁣
• P3-P6 Math Concept Mastery Workshop⁣
Don't wait too long to consider because their PSLE Oral Workshop is already FULL!⁣
⁣
Find out more at www.tenopy.co!
